/)\n\n### 尺寸\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"15rem\"](passwordgloo/eg97cavm/)\n\n### 内边距\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"32rem\"](passwordgloo/pmoekhg0/)\n\n### 内减模式\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"17rem\"](passwordgloo/q9agjr0w/)\n\n### 外边距\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"13rem\"](passwordgloo/vskq9dyn/)\n\n::: warning 清除默认内外边距\n\n通配符选择器消耗资源大，能不用就不用\n\n:::\n\n```css\n* {\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 0;\n}\n```\n\n#### 版心居中\n\n@[jsfiddle tab=\"css, html,result\" height=\"12rem\"](passwordgloo/3hxdpvtz/)\n\n#### 常见问题\n\n::: normal-demo 合并问题\n\n```html\n<div class=\"one\">11</div>\n<div class=\"two\">22</div>\n```\n\n```css\ndiv {\n    width: 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n    background-color: pink;\n}\n\n.one {\n    /* margin-bottom: 50px; */\n    margin-bottom: 60px;\n}\n\n.two {\n    margin-top: 50px;\n}\n```\n\n:::\n\n::: normal-demo 塌陷问题\n\n```html\n<div class=\"father\">\n    <div class=\"son\">son</div>\n</div>\n```\n\n```css\n.father {\n    width: 300px;\n    height: 300px;\n    background-color: pink;\n    /* padding-top: 50px; */\n    /* 如果设计稿没有border, 不能使用这个解决办法 */\n    /* border: 1px solid #000; */\n\n    /* overflow: hidden; */\n}\n\n.son {\n    width: 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n    background-color: skyblue;\n\n    margin-top: 50px;\n\n    display: inline-block;\n}\n```\n\n:::","excerpt":"","tasklists":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"优先级","slug":"优先级","link":"#优先级","children":[{"level":3,"title":"权重计算","slug":"权重计算","link":"#权重计算","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"标签选择器","slug":"标签选择器","link":"#标签选择器","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"权重叠加每位不存在进制","slug":"权重叠加每位不存在进制","link":"#权重叠加每位不存在进制","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"权重相同此时比较层叠性","slug":"权重相同此时比较层叠性","link":"#权重相同此时比较层叠性","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"全是继承的特殊情况","slug":"全是继承的特殊情况","link":"#全是继承的特殊情况","children":[]}]},{"level":2,"title":"盒子模型","slug":"盒子模型","link":"#盒子模型","children":[{"level":3,"title":"边框","slug":"边